welp i cant believe this year at SNHU is over... sam, wade, anthony, kevin, and i were the only ones left today!! sad isn't it!! but we had a good 'last night' together (instead of studying for all of our 8am finals hahaha) but i just wanted to post a cute away message that sam had up today, i couldn't say it better sam!!!!

   

Seefoammgreentux: as the realization that we are going home, and the year is over there comes a very unexplainable saddness. the Mac Attack is slowly disesembling. We are leaving these walls, the last time all of us will ever live together. Funny huh? 20 people who knew nothing about each other in september are now so upset about not seeing each other for a little while. I am going to miss you all SO much!!! To those of you who are questioning if you are coming back next year, YOU BETTER, and for those of you who we know shall never attend another class at snhu, or never did, you best get up here and visit us all! I hope everyone has a good summer, and I love you guys!! :'(

 

  

Good Times Mac Attack!!! Dont be sad we will see eachother next year, except for you Keith, and you ARE coming to visit!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

Have a great summer everyone and see ya next year, and for those of you who I wont, you better call , you know the number!
